      {
        "step_no": 2,
        "text": "Heat a wok or large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. Add half the neutral oil. When hot but not smoking, pour in beaten eggs and let set briefly, then scramble gently until just-cooked but still soft. Transfer eggs to a plate and set aside.",
